high_descs: Move to the small space in between the toilet and the vanity.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll off of the floor.
Turn around and move to the white dresser that is on the left.
Open the bottom drawer and place the empty roll inside. Close the drawer.
Move across the room to the left side of the bath tub.
Pick up the full roll of toilet paper.
Turn around and move across the room to the white dresser in front of you.
Open the bottom drawer and place the full roll of tissue inside.  Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two  tissue rolls - one empty, one full - to the inside of the bottom drawer of the white dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the right side of the toilet, then turn right to face the space between the toilet and sink.
Pick up the empty toilet paper tube from the floor between the wastebasket and sink cabinet.
Face the opposite direction, then go to the white cabinet on your left.
Put the empty tube into the back right corner of the bottom drawer.
Turn around and cross the room to  the back left corner of the tub.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper between the tub and the white hanging towels.
Turn around and return to the white cabinet.
Put the roll of toilet paper into the bottom drawer, to the left of the empty tube.
anns.task_desc: Put an empty toilet paper tube and roll of toilet paper into a bathroom drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the toilet, then turn right and face the red bin.
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the ground to the right of the bin.
Turn around and veer right to the white cabinet.
Place the toilet paper roll in the bottom drawer of the cabinet on the right side.
Turn around and walk to the far side of the bath tub.
Pick up the toilet paper roll of the edge of the bath tub, near the window.
Turn around and walk back to the white cabinet.
Place the toilet paper roll in the bottom drawer to the left of the other roll.
anns.task_desc: Place two toilet paper rolls in a cabinet.
